#### 13-17. **Additional Issues** (MEDIUM severity)

13. **Line 1453-1454:** Storing URL in JS property (`_downloadUrl`) is non-standard, use `data-` attributes
14. **Line 1246:** Audio player created globally, should be per-job to avoid conflicts
15. **Line 640:** Slider event listener not removed, leaks on repeated init
16. **Line 955:** `variationsCancelBtn` listener not removed
17. **Line 1047:** `ended` event listener never removed from Audio objects

