## Fix Priority

| Issue | Severity | Impact | Fix Complexity |
|-------|----------|--------|----------------|
| **Polling Memory Leak** | CRITICAL | Server overload, browser crash | MEDIUM (add abort controllers) |
| **Audio Not Disposed** | CRITICAL | Memory exhaustion | LOW (add cleanup) |
| **DOM Thrashing** | CRITICAL | UI freezes | MEDIUM (use DocumentFragment) |
| **No Request Cancellation** | CRITICAL | Server exhaustion | MEDIUM (AbortController) |
| **Event Listener Duplication** | CRITICAL | Browser freeze, DDoS | LOW (check before adding) |
| **Missing Timeout Errors** | HIGH | Poor UX | LOW (add error types) |
| **Unprotected Mutations** | HIGH | Race conditions | LOW (immutable updates) |
| **Excessive Status Updates** | HIGH | Unnecessary reflows | LOW (debounce) |
| **Modal Not Cleaned** | HIGH | Memory leak | LOW (call remove()) |
| **No Request Dedup** | HIGH | Wasted requests | LOW (add guard) |
| **Unsafe Escaping** | HIGH | XSS vulnerability | MEDIUM (use DOMPurify) |
| **Progress Not Reset** | HIGH | Stale UI | LOW (use toggle) |

